net.varkhan.base.management.monitor
Interface MonitorParameter<P extends java.lang.Enum<P>,V,T>

Type Parameters:
P - an Enum identifying the parameters
V - the type of the main monitored value

All Superinterfaces:
Monitor<V>
public interface MonitorParameter<P extends java.lang.Enum<P>,V,T>
extends Monitor<V>

A monitor whose value is governed by several parameters.

A monitor that links a main monitored value point to several named components, either source or product of the main value.
